title: Ambaum Place 2 # 205- Studio
posting_body: Come check out the new Ambaum Place Apartments II in Burien!
This is a beautiful brand-new building with controlled access, playground and picnic area and fitness center!
You'll love your new home, with exceptionally tall ceilings, open floor plans, and lots of light!
All studio apartment homes have wood laminate flooring throughout.
This studio apartment has everything you need, to include new stove, refrigerator, dishwasher, and built-in microwave!
Each unit also has large private balcony or patio, as well as your own full size washer & dryer.
These well-made apartments feature LED lighting, and triple-pane windows that offer energy efficiency and sound control!
Enjoy state of the art insulation ... save energy while lowering your utility costs!
Ambaum Place is a great location for the commuter!
Quick access to I5, 405, 509 and I90.
Only 10 minutes from the Seatac Airport, 20 minutes from Seattle, but also close to restaurants and grocery stores (PCC and Trader Joes included) and 15 minutes from Westfield Mall!
Also, located on the bus lines (120, 128, 130)
Call or email today to schedule a private showing of your new home!
Off street parking and additional storage also available****
